Aaron Hernandez was sentenced to life in prison without parole for the 2013 murder of Odin Lloyd on Wednesday . 
  He is starting his sentence at MCI Cedar Junction prison in Walpole, Massachusetts . 
  The prison is just a mile and a half from Gillette Stadium where he used to play for the New England Patriots . 
  Hernandez was booked at the prison on Wednesday after he was found guilty of murder in the death of Lloyd . 
  He will be housed at the maximum-security prison for the first two years of his sentence . 
  On Wednesday he was taken to the prison after being sentenced to a life sentence for the murder of Lloyd  . 
 